# Task 1: File Permissions

## Description
Create a file named `aryan.txt`, assign permissions (read, write, execute) to different user categories (owner, group, others), and practice changing permissions using `chmod`.

---

## Instructions

### 1. Create the File
```sh
touch aryan.txt
